- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is another possible category as the Frechet distance is a discrete metric that measures the similarity between two curves based on their discrete points. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of the Frechet distance for comparing GPS trajectories, which is a common task in AI applications such as location-based services and autonomous vehicles. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also a possible category as the paper mentions the use of the Frechet distance for comparing handwritten characters, which is a common task in computer vision and pattern recognition.
